lications/uz/359225.jpg" alt="" style="margin-left:27%;box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; clear: both; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;" class="fr-fic fr-dib"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><br></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Kasb tanlashda inson bir necha omillardan kelib chiqib qaror qabul qiladi. Ushbu omillar insonning o&rsquo;z qiziqsihlari va ehtiyojlari, mahorat va qobiliyatlari, ta&rsquo;lim va o&rsquo;qish imkoniyatlari, bozor ehtiyojlari va ish toppish imkoniyatlari, moliyaviy daromad, shaxsiy hayot va ish muvozanati hamda kelajakdagi rivojlanish imkoniyatlari kabilarni o&rsquo;z ichiga olishi mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Mazkur omillar orasida moliyaviy daromad olish imkoniyatlari har bir kishi uchun eng muhim omillardan biri hisoblanadi. Ko&rsquo;pchilik yuqori daromad keltiradigan va barqaror iqtisodiy kelajak va&rsquo;da qiladigan kasblarni afzal ko&rsquo;rishadi. O&rsquo;zbekistonda hozirda qaysi sohalarda yuqori daromad olish mumkin?</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2022-yilda</strong> iqtisodiyotda band bo&lsquo;lganlar soni&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">13,7 million</strong> kishini, o&lsquo;rtacha oylik nominal ish haqi miqdori esa&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,2 million</strong> so&lsquo;mni tashkil etgan. Moliya (o&rsquo;rtacha 10 million so&rsquo;m), axborot texnologiyalari (6,7 million so&rsquo;m), transport (3,9 million so&rsquo;m) va sanoat (3,7 million so&rsquo;m) kabi sohalarda o&rsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqi respublikadagi o&lsquo;rtacha ko&lsquo;rsatkichdan sezilarli yuqori bo&rsquo;lsa, yashash va ovqatlanish (1,5 million so&rsquo;m) hamda savdo (2 million so&rsquo;m) kabi xizmat ko&rsquo;rsatish sohalarida rasmiy ravishda hisoblangan nominal ish haqi miqdori ancha pastligicha saqlanib qolmoqda. Shu o&rsquo;rinda ta&rsquo;kidlab &nbsp;lozimki, o&rsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqi Respublika bo&rsquo;yicha o&rsquo;rtacha ish haqidan kam bo&rsquo;lgan sohalarda iqtisodiyotda band bo&lsquo;lganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">63 foizi</strong> mehnat qiladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">2016 yilda<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>eng yuqori o&rsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqi (moliya &ndash; 2 million so&rsquo;m) va eng past o&rsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqi (yashash va ovqatlanish &ndash; 612 ming so&rsquo;m) o&rsquo;rtasidagi farq 3,3 barobarni tashkil etgan bo&rsquo;lsa, 2022 yilda ushbu ko&rsquo;rsatkich 6,6 barobarga yetdi. 2022 yilda moliya sohasida o&rsquo;rtacha nominal ish haqi 2016 yilga nisbatan 5 barobarga oshgan bo&rsquo;lsa, yashash va ovqatlanish bo&rsquo;yicha xizmatlar sohasida ushbu ko&rsquo;rsatkich 2,5 barobarni tashkil etgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2016-2022 yillarda o&rsquo;rtacha nominal ish haqi</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image-20231212162840-1.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: 653px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 974px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Yashash va ovqatlanish hamda savdo xizmatlari sohasida nomial ish haqi miqdorining ancha past darajada saqlanib qolayotgani mazkur sohalarda yashirin iqtisodiyot hajmining yuqoriligidan ham dalolat beradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Rivojlanayotgan davlatlarda nisbatan yuqori inflatsiya sharoitida turli tarmoqlar kesimida o&#39;rtacha nominal ish haqi miqdorlarini taqqoslashda, oylik ish haqining real o&#39;sish sur&#39;atlari juda muhim ahamiyat kasb etadi. Turli tarmoqlarda ish haqining o&#39;sishi har xil bo&#39;lishi mumkin. Biroq, inflatsiya darajasi barcha sektorlarga bir xil ta&#39;sir ko&#39;rsatadi. Shu sababli, real daromadlar o&rsquo;sishi tarmoqlar kesimida qanchalik farq qilishini tushunish muhimdir.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">2022 yilda respublika bo&rsquo;yicha o&rsquo;rtacha real oylik ish haqi 2016 yilga nisbatan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">52,6 foizga&nbsp;</strong>oshdi. Tahlil qilinayotgan davr mobaynida real o&lsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqining eng yuqori o&lsquo;sish sur&rsquo;atlari moliya (<a name="_Hlk151710142" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">167,5</strong></a><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;foiz</strong>), axborot texnologiyalari (<a name="_Hlk151710153" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">91,0&nbsp;</strong></a><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">foiz</strong>), qishloq xo&rsquo;jaligi (63 foiz), sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash (<a name="_Hlk151710169" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">44,2&nbsp;</strong></a><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">foiz</strong>) hamda transport va logistika (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40,0 foiz</strong>) sohalarida kuzatildi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Savdo xizmatlari sohasida &nbsp;o&lsquo;rtacha real ish haqi miqdori &nbsp;deyarli o&rsquo;zgarmagan bo&rsquo;lsa (<a name="_Hlk151710206" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">real o&rsquo;sish -&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">0,24&nbsp;</strong></a><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">foiz</strong>), qurilish (<a name="_Hlk151710224" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16,0&nbsp;</strong></a><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">foiz</strong>) va san&rsquo;at (<a name="_Hlk151710237" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">17,1</strong></a><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;foiz</strong>) kabi tarmoqlarda ish haqining sotib olish qobiliyati nisbatan sekin o&lsquo;sgani aniqlandi. Mazkur sohalarda real ish haqi o&rsquo;sish sur&rsquo;atlarining nisbatan past darajada saqlanib qolayotgani yashirin iqtisodiyot ko&rsquo;lami bilan birgalikda ishchilar va ish beruvchilar o&rsquo;rtasida ish haqi borasida muzokaralar qilish imkoniyatlarining pastligi bilan ham izohlanishi mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;">1-rasm</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Real ish haqining o&lsquo;zgarishi</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">(2016-yil narxlariga nisbatan inflatsiyani hisobga olgan holda)</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image-20231212162840-2.png" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: 919px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 1119px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">Manba: Statistika agentligi ma&rsquo;lumotlari</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Raqamlashtirish va bozor munosabatlarining jadal rivojlanishi sharoitida mehnat resurslarining mobilligini oshirish juda dolzarb ahamiyatga ega bo&lsquo;lib bormoqda. Bugungi zamonaviy texnologiyalar rivojlanib borayotgan davrda o&rsquo;z kasbini yuqori malaka talab etmaydigan, lekin ko&rsquo;proq daromad keltiradigan kasblarga o&lsquo;zgartirish oddiy va kamxarajat hodisa bo&rsquo;lishga ulgurdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Hozirda O&lsquo;zbekistonda moliya, IT va logistika yo&rsquo;nalishlari bo&rsquo;yicha o&rsquo;quv kurslari taklif etayotgan 45 ta o&lsquo;quv markazlari tahlili shuni ko&rsquo;rsatmoqdaki, biroz vaqt va ta&rsquo;lim uchun katta bo&rsquo;lmagan miqdorda investitsiya qilish har qanday insonning moliyaviy daromadlarini oshirishga hamda iqtisodiyotda ish haqlari o&rsquo;rtasidagi tafovutni qisqartirishga xizmat qilishi mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><a name="_Hlk152669989" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">1.&nbsp;</a>Moliya yo&rsquo;nalishlarida o&lsquo;qitishni taklif qiluvchi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">10 ta</strong> ta&rsquo;lim markazlarida o&rsquo;quv kurslarining o&lsquo;rtacha davomiyligi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4 oy</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ni,</strong> o&rsquo;qish uchun oylik to&lsquo;lov miqdori esa o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1 million</strong> so&lsquo;mni tashkil etadi Ushbu kurslar moliya asoslari, ish haqini hisoblash va tashkilotning umumiy hisobini yuritishni o&lsquo;rgatadi. Shunday qilib, mazkur moliya mutaxassisligi bo&lsquo;yicha o&lsquo;qib, ushbu sohada ishga joylashgan shaxslar respublika bo&rsquo;yicha o&lsquo;rtacha ish haqi miqdorida maosh olgan taqdirda, ko&lsquo;pi bilan 1,5 oy ichida ta&rsquo;limga sarflagan xarajatlarini (4 million so&rsquo;m) qoplab, qisqa muddatlarda o&rsquo;z daromadlarini sezilarli darajada oshirishlari mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">2.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Axborot texnologiyalari (IT) mutaxassisligini</strong> o&lsquo;rganish moliya mutaxassisligiga nisbatan biroz ko&lsquo;proq vaqt talab etadi. Axborot texnologiyalari sohasida kurslarni taklif etayotgan 20 ta o&lsquo;quv markazlarida ta&rsquo;lim olish imkoniyatlari tahlili natijalariga ko&rsquo;ra, hozirda IT yo&lsquo;nalishi bo&lsquo;yicha kurslarning o&lsquo;rtacha davomiyligi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">6,5 oyni</strong>, o&lsquo;rtacha narxi oyiga 1<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">,5 million</strong> so&lsquo;mni tashkil qiladi. Moliya yo&rsquo;nalishi bo&rsquo;yicha kurslardan farqli o&lsquo;laroq, IT kurslarida onlayn shaklda o&lsquo;qitish keng tarqalgan. Ushbu kurslarda ta&rsquo;lim olish orqali veb-saytlar yaratish, kodlar yozish va kiberxavfsizlik ko&lsquo;nikmalarini egallash mumkin. Binobarin, mazkur kurslarni tamomlab, ishga qabul qilinganidan so&lsquo;ng, o&lsquo;qitish xarajatlari o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2-3 oy</strong> ichida qoplash imkoniyati mavjud.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">3.&nbsp;Bugungi kunda logistika sohasida o&lsquo;qishni taklif etayotgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">15 ta</strong> o&lsquo;quv markazlarida dispetcherlikka o&lsquo;qish muddati o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1 oyni, o&rsquo;quv&nbsp;</strong>kurslarining narxi esa o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2,3 mln.</strong> so&lsquo;mni tashkil etadi. Ba&rsquo;zi o&lsquo;quv markazlari kurslarni a&rsquo;lo natijalar bilan tugatgan bitiruvchilarga ish o&lsquo;rni ham taklif etadi. Bugungi kunda logistika sohasi mutaxassislari o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">6 million</strong> so&lsquo;m oylik maosh olishmoqda.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ta&rsquo;kidlash joizki, logistika sohasida o&lsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqi tez sur&rsquo;atlar bilan o&lsquo;sib bormoqda. Shu bilan birga sohada masofaviy bandlik ham keng tarqalgan. Masalan,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">olx.uz</strong> saytida (2023 yil noyabr oyi ma&#39;lumotlariga ko&lsquo;ra) logistika yo&lsquo;nalishi bo&lsquo;yicha keltirilgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1000 dan</strong> ortiq bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining 30 foizi masofaviy ish hisoblanadi. Shuningdek, bu sohada ishlash katta tajribani talab etmaydi. Bularning barchasini hisobga olgan holda, kasbini o&lsquo;zgartirishni istovchilar uchun logistika yo&lsquo;nalish keng imkoniyatlar tadqim etishi mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Raqamlashtirish va bozor munosabatlarining rivojlanishi bilan bir qatorda, mehnat resurslarining mobilligi ham oshib bormoqda. Shuningdek, sun&rsquo;iy intellektning tez sur&rsquo;atlarda rivojlanayotganligi mehnat bozorida ishchilarning moslashuvchanlik va mobillik ko&lsquo;nikmalarini shakllantirishni talab etmoqda.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Xizmatlarni rivojlantirish va<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">bandlikni ta&rsquo;minlash loyihasi</strong></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;">658</span></div></div></div></header><div style="color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;"><br></div>
